Suukie walks into the base..... "hi, Liono, i was a little harsh i thought i
would come back though....i found these outside, Plintissa left these for
you behind...." he said..he handed the box to Liono..it had the note in it
and had the 3 weapons she took before and it had the adta chips....which she
never did to give to the Predacons....in her note it said that would be
better if they went their seperate ways.....Suukie looked at himself in the
mirror and walked into the CR Chamber..... "i'm still with you Liono, i
never left you know..." he said....taking a snooze in the CR Chamber....
